data.description: Introducing this beautiful 5 bed-3 bath home, situated in a desirable neighborhood. As you step onto the property, the breathtaking views of Pikes Peak Mountain will greet you. Step inside and prepare to be amazed by the abundance of upgrades is in store for you. From the floor to the ceiling, the bathrooms are adorned with impeccable tile that adds a touch of luxury.The soft close drawers and cabinets throughout the house are as functional as they are elegant. Prepare to fall in love with the quartz farmhouse kitchen sink, perfect for all your cooking and cleaning needs. Not just the interiors, even the garage will leave you impressed. With a finished drywalled space and an epoxy floor, your vehicles will rest in comfort and style. Plus, with the extended driveway and custom outdoor stairs, parking will never be an issue for you or your guests. This stunning stamped concrete patio is just waiting for you to host unforgettable gatherings with family and friends. Vinyl flooring on the main floor and upgraded carpet downstairs complete the perfect blend of elegance and comfort. House included a Culligan RO water system and a water softener throughout the house, ensuring clean and pure water every single day. The attention to detail is evident in every aspect of this home. From upgraded doors, baseboards, light fixtures, and hardware to a custom kitchen backsplash that adds that unique touch, no stone has been left unturned in creating a space that is truly remarkable. If you're a culinary enthusiast, the gas cooktop will become your new best friend, elevating your cooking experience to new heights. Don't wait another moment to make your dream a reality.This stunning home with all its luxurious upgrades is calling your name.
